com.ualberta.cs.alfred

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ualberta.cs.alfred.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    The user class holds all of the common data needed as both a rider and a driver. All users will be contained on the Elastic Search server where they will pulled when a user logs in to the local device.
    See Also:
    RiderInfo, DriverInfo
